<br>
My primary MA is pretty catch-as-catch-can on IP distribution. She's a bit of a mess, but still perfectly viable. Lately, she's had more focus and has improved quite a bit. Might help if I actually played her more, but I like her as she is. Mainly, she spent on combat skills and nano whenever I felt the need. Basic stats tended to get ignored when inconveniant, and this has caused me some not inconsiderable hassle with implants later on in life. That's the one thing I would change: keep basics up like INT and STR/AGI.<br>
<br>
My secondary MA (nanomage) is a good deal more focused and tends to be much stronger at specific levels than my solitus. Now, she does have odd requirements for IP, but the fundamental goal is the same. Here I keep INT maxed to keep the nanos perking along (some) without specifically spending IP on them. When they're near a new nano, or I feel something is getting weak, then I blow IP for what I need. Everything else goes into combat skills and maxing important basic stats (AGI, STA, INT, PSY, body dev--like I said, she's a bit odd). <br>
<br>
Also, plan implants around the same goals. You want heals and crit boosters--bio met, sens imp, psy mod, and T&amp;S. Short term goals of new heals, and a long term goal of the next crit booster. Plan and spend accordingly.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/unaazareth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Naazareth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Ninja Wanna-Be</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#660000>(9/27/02 3:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=508.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re: Re:</span><hr size=1> ah, thank you very much for the information. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=508.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=508.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=508.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=508.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.threadControl?topicID=508.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.subsc